Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:06.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kano.
Comment: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:22.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,some sound here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:24.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:24.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:25.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:26.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:29.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko pikopiko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:04.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you might have this bruise for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:07.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've caused you much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:10.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, Kunisaki-kun, Kamio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:11.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:14.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't mind.
Comment: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:20.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: It's not a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:24.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It started when Kano was still a little girl.
Comment: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:27.80,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:31.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was the first summer after our mother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:41.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, balloons!
Comment: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:44.06,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,BALLOONS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:45.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:48.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, if I bought one, would I be able to fly through the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:50.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If one balloon could lift a person, the stall would have flown away by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:55.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, you're so smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:03:01.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, that means I can fly in the sky if I have lots of  balloons, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:04.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes, maybe then you could fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:10.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can only afford one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:14.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's one balloon, we'll just have to blow it up really big!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:18.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do that, it'll be able to lift up much more weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:21.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And we won't be able to buy anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:22.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:27.07,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,BALLOONS\NTARGET
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:27.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Comment: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:27.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:29.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, thank you, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:33.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kano always wanted to fly through the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:39.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because she believed she could see her mother there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:45.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I told her that her mother was in the sky, watching over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:52.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Neither Father nor I could tell her
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:04:01.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that her mother was no longer around anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:01.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:03.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:48.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what happened?
Comment: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:48.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: What happened afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:50.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:54.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's playing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:59.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We put the feather back and went home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:13.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't go to where Mommy is anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:16.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The following morning, Kano started acting strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:18.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She became afraid of bright lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:21.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and she started wandering around outside in a daze
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:24.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and mumbling nonsense to herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:30.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One night, Kano was gone before I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:32.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After I rushed to look for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:35.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I found her in the examination room, pressing a scalpel to her wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:36.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught her in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:39.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so it wasn't serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:42.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I realized then she wasn't Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:45.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like someone else was pretending to be Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a case of multiple personalities?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:51.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It might have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:55.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a magical bandana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:06:01.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep wearing until you're an adult, you'll be able to use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:05.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, whatever happens, never take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:09.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:09.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were the one who gave Kano the bandana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she ever tried to unconsciously cut her wrist again,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:16.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she'd see the bandana and come to her senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:16.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:20.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano doesn't remember it much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:23.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There never was any such thing as magic.
Comment: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:24.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: There was never such a thing as magic. Which phrases better?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:27.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to follow in my father's footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:32.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if I became a doctor, I'd be able to cure Kano's illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:34.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that feather that Kano touched?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:36.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:39.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently it's been there at the shrine for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:42.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the shrine-keeper doesn't know the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:45.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pehrpas it's the curse of that feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:50.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a doctor, I can't accept that kind of explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:54.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's possible that the feather was a psychological trigger for her illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:59.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, Kano was suffering under a lot of stress after losing her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:02.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was probably the root cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:05.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to Kirishima-san's place today too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:08.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:08.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my job there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:11.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I will go visit Kano later too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:14.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:15.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad you made a new friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, I had another dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:18.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:21.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream of flying through the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:25.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In this dream, I was traveling further and further back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:31.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, I was mourning in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.64,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were mourning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:39.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, my body was soaring through the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:43.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was overwhelmed by sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.73,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered why,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:52.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,surrounded by such beautiful, comforting breezes, I felt so sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:56.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:56.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with you personally.
Comment: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:56.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Awkward phrase above.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:57.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're not smiling, I also feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:01.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.78,0:08:03.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, just keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:06.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:20.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:25.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:31.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:31.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:33.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was about to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:35.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you picking up stuff like that to collect garbage or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:37.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:40.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Collecting interesting things from places like this is my hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:42.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the most pathetic hobby ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:46.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:50.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You get to play, day in, day out. You're in a very enviable position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:54.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty much like that too, aren't you, Yukito Kunisaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:56.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a proper job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:09:00.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I'm on my way right now to my job to work hard.
Comment: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:00.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Some sound I can't hear. Ony? or Oy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:02.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:04.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:07.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:12.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:19.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that, by any chance, Tohno's mom?
Comment: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:00.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Some sound I can't hear. Ony? or Oy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:21.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:24.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:37.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi looks sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:38.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:40.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, call Minagi over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:42.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's lonely being by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:45.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:45.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:46.71,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohno!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:59.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:09:59.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:09:59.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:09:59.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:02.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just taking a walk with Michiru.
Comment: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:03.43,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma Cycling Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:03.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:03.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:06.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you with Michiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:11.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:17.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Michiru say anything about the person who was with me just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:19.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:19.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't say anything in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:22.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is your mother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:25.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:30.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I once helped her with a big cart of groceries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:34.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, the two of you are rather similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:38.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a fragment of that person's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:39.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:43.90,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko pikopiko piko piko piko piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:47.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away, Potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:50.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I'll scrub you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:51.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko pikopiko... Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be in high spirits.
Comment: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:57.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Better phrase than 'high spirits'?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:59.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yukito-kun. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. It seems that I caused you troubled yesterday too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:02.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:04.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:08.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you came, Kunisaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:21.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a lot of work for you to do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:24.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kano-san taking a nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:24.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:27.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told her to rest, because of what happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:30.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for her to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:31.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check up on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:35.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:45.87,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yukito-kun, I am writing this to you because I think you'll believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:48.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've finally decided to go to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:53.03,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a feeling that it will make everyone happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:57.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a feeling that I will meet the girl you are looking for too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:12:01.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know how long it will take,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:05.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I will definitely bring her to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:08.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd be grateful if you could help Onee-chan until I return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:08.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know she is under a lot of stress.
Comment: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:09.29,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: She's actually really pushing herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:13.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}P.S. I'm really sorry about the bruise on your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:22.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:23.07,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Pikopikopikopiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:24.61,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopikopikopikopiko pikopikopikopikopikopiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:26.37,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko. Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:27.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:30.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko Piko Piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:35.48,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:42.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:43.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:45.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no external wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:47.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about the blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.23,0:12:48.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no sign of bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:51.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem to be life-threatening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:53.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but what on earth happened?
Comment: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:53.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: 'on earth' -> 'exactly'
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:56.60,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she tried to go up to the sky from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:13:06.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:07.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:11.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:13.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, my emotions are acting up,
Comment: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:13.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,better word for acting up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:19.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,like I'm nostalgic... or sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:22.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lay Kano down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunisaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:48.39,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is Shiraho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:51.15,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please listen to my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:56.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remember it was a beautiful autumn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:01.20,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My husband and I had our first child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:05.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She had a birthmark on her right wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:10.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The villagers said it was ominous, but we never paid them any attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:16.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Yakumo cried, I sang him a lullaby that I had learned from my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:22.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yakumo would always stop crying, but that day, she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:39.13,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt that the feather was a charm sent by God for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:59.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A war started, and my husband, like many others, never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:11.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone in this village pick up a shining feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:15.41,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is cursed! Anyone who has touched it should step forward and confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:19.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That night, I fled from the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:37.96,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, I arrived at this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:46.94,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The chief priest of the shrine was very kind to us outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:54.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I felt that Yakumo and I would be able to start a new life in this peaceful village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:01.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, that summer, an epidemic spread through the village, killing many.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:08.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Priest, how is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The worst is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His fever will come down in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:17.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the villagers believe the two of you brought the epidemic to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:19.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:24.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake to invite the two of you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:27.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, we worship a divine idol.
Comment: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:27.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Here we worship the miko-gami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.01,0:16:31.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The idol gives a sign to those who bring bad fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the villagers discover her birthmark, they will demand her to be sacrificed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:41.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me to sacrifice him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:42.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In this land, we have always averted disasters by doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:50.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This child is my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:53.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the only treasure my husband left me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:55.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:58.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you will be killed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:00.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:00.00,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:22.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:22.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:24.74,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What mother would kill her own child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:29.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it might destroy the world, what mother could bear to kill her own child?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:38.51,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, somehow, save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:40.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:02.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.78,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:10.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:13.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm already full!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:17.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:25.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'll go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:29.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:30.04,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And Potato too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:32.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And a new friend I've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:34.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:38.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he's looking for a girl in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:41.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of wish that I were that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:45.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If things are too hard for you, you can come with me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:51.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:58.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember much about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:04.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I might have cut your life short,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:05.70,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:10.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for giving birth to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:11.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:14.24,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:21.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:21.32,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't have wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:23.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so live happily down there.
Comment: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:30.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono ko no kawaisa kagirinaya\NThere is no end to the ways this child is so dear
Comment: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:39.90,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten ni tatoeba hoshi no kazu\NLike the number of stars in the heavens
Comment: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:45.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yama dewa ki no kazu, kaya no kazu\NThe number of trees in the mountains
Comment: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:49.21,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yama dewa ki no kazu, kaya no kazu\NThe number of grasses in the field
Comment: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:59.16,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Obana karukaya, hagi, kikyou\NFlowering broomsedge, bush clover, bellflowers
Comment: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:04.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana kusa, chigusa no kazu yorimo\NMore than the flowers of autumn
Comment: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:08.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana kusa, chigusa no kazu yorimo\NMore than the number of all the flowering plants
Comment: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:17.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Daijina kono ko ga nenne suru\NMy precious child is sleeping
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:22.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamio-san, you saw it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:25.95,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:34.56,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:36.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:37.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:41.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.14,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:54.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:54.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:56.92,Air Dialogue - top,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko piko piko piko piko piko piko piko piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:12.43,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what was that feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:14.06,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Comment: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:15.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:17.77,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, I met Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:20.11,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:23.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't go to where she was,
Comment: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:23.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alt: I couldn't go with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:27.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was able to thank her, just like Yukito-kun told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to Yukito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.92,0:21:32.59,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:34.68,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:41.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:57.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it soar into the sky for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.84,0:21:58.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:41.15,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.52,0:23:43.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bubbles are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.62,0:23:46.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're empty, just like the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.29,0:23:53.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a real bother, so I'm always playing by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.46,0:23:57.26,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.80,0:24:00.63,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother couldn't accept reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.63,0:24:04.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so she chose to live in her dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.90,0:24:07.37,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a use for wings that cannot fly?
Comment: 0,0:24:08.84,0:24:10.17,Air Typesetting,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 5